<Base title="API Multiplayer Chat Room" description="Unity Netcode lobby + real-time chat demo.">
  <h1>API Multiplayer Chat Room</h1>
  <div class="prose">
    <p>This Unity project demonstrates networked chat functionality. I built a lobby system with Unity Netcode for GameObjects and implemented real-time chat so players can host and join sessions and communicate seamlessly.</p>
    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Host/Join lobby flow</li>
      <li>Real-time chat sync</li>
      <li>Connection status and basic UI</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Base>
